ds_cdwtriage.description: Issues are New and have no target release set
ds_cdwtriage.jql: project = JBDS AND status = New AND ('Target Release' is EMPTY OR 'CDW release' in ('?'))

ds_lockdown.jql: ((project = JBIDE AND fixVersion in ( %(jbide_lockdown_version)s )) OR (project = JBDS AND fixVersion in ( %(jbds_lockdown_version)s )))

ds_maint.jql: ((project = JBIDE AND fixVersion in ( %(jbide_maint_versions)s )) OR (project = JBDS AND fixVersion in ( %(jbds_maint_versions)s )))

ds_master.description: Current project+versions for JBIDE/JBDS master stream
ds_master.jql: ((project = JBIDE AND fixVersion in ( %(jbide_master_versions)s )) OR (project = JBDS AND fixVersion in ( %(jbds_master_versions)s )))

ds_mystuff.description: Issues assigned to current user or in a component lead by current user.

ds_needpmack.description: Product manager have not yet approved a jira with a target release
ds_needpmack.jql: 'Target Release' is not EMPTY AND 'CDW pm_ack' = '?' AND resolution = Unresolved

ds_next.jql: ((project = JBIDE AND fixVersion in ( %(jbide_next_version)s )) OR (project = JBDS AND fixVersion in ( %(jbds_lockdown_version)s )))

ds_decisions_maint.description: DECISIONs for current project+versions for JBIDE/JBDS maintenance
ds_decisions_maint.jql: ((project = JBIDE AND fixVersion in ( %(jbide_maint_versions)s )) OR (project = JBDS AND fixVersion in ( %(jbds_maint_versions)s ))) AND comment ~ DECISION

ds_decisions_master.description: DECISIONs for current project+versions for JBIDE/JBDS master stream
ds_decisions_master.jql: ((project = JBIDE AND fixVersion in ( %(jbide_master_versions)s )) OR (project = JBDS AND fixVersion in ( %(jbds_master_versions)s ))) AND comment ~ DECISION
